txt.en: Barricades can be found at Norwarden in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should destroy barricades at Norwarden.
Barricades found at Norwarden should be destroyed in order weaken the defences of your foes within the Wildwood.
Barricades can be found at Norwarden in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should destroy barricades at Norwarden.
Foes of the Free Peoples have fortified the tower of Norwarden within the Wildwood. Destroying the barricades here should weaken the Norwarden defences.
